Interface NewListIP

All Superinterfaces:
ListIP, NewScalarIP, ScalarIP
All Known Subinterfaces:
AdvancedIP
All Known Implementing Classes:
IterativeParallelism, IterativeParallelism
public interface NewListIP extends NewScalarIP, ListIP
List iterative parallelism support with sparse data.

Each method of this interface takes an extra positive integer step. Only each step-th element of the input list should be used (counting from 0).

Author:
Georgiy Korneev (kgeorgiy@kgeorgiy.info)
